Selection for positional stock :
  Step-0 : Choose a stock
  Step-1 : Check price is near to 52-week low
  Step-2 : Look at the fundamentals(like ROE,P/E,EPS,Dividend etc)
  Step-3 : Look financial record(like profit, revenue,etc)
  Step-3 : Shareholding(promoter,foreign institutions,mutual fund)
  Step-4 : Go to online tool for advice(ticker tape, ticker tape etc)


